pageProduct.name: Swisse Kids Probiotic & Prebiotic Gummies 45 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Kids Probiotic & Prebiotic Gummies are a deliciously convenient way to get 2 Billion CFU of probiotics, plus a prebiotic source of fibre that feeds good bacteria in the gut.

Size: 45 Pack

KEY FEATURES

• * 2 Billion good bacteria per serve
• * contains Inulin (from chicory root fibre) a natural prebiotic and source of fibre that feeds gut bacteria
• * No added sugar or sweetener
• * Natural raspberry flavour
• * Great tasting for fussy eaters

Ingredients

Ingredients: Chicory root fibre (60%), Water, Stabilisers (Pectin, Agar Agar), Tapioca Starch, Acidity regulators (Citric acid, trisodium citrate), Bacillus Coagulans Spores (0.39%), Colour (black carrot concentrate), Natural raspberry flavour, Glazing agent (Carnauba wax)

Directions

Chew 2 gummies daily. Do not swallow whole.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Chew 2 gummies daily. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct heat
